Note on data provenance
-----------------------
The data in `data/` is derived from publicly posted content on Reddit's r/ChangeMyView
subreddit, collected via the Arctic Shift tool/API in accordance with Reddit's terms of
service for academic research. The release does not include private communications or
annotation labels from our human validation study.
